txt.en:
'Unlike Haudh Arantar, where the Angmarim are just ransacking and destroying the crypt, the searching at Haudh Eldacar seems to be much more methodical. Very little has been removed thus far.

'Whatever they are looking for there must be of great importance to their purpose here in Ann√∫minas.

'We must delay them while we discover what their goal is. If you were to drive out the party currently searching within, it would buy us valuable time.'
'I do not yet know their ultimate purpose, but I know that we have set it back, if only ever so slightly.'
'You must delay them while we search for the reason they are here.'
Angmar has taken an interest in Haudh Eldacar.
Haudh Eldacar is south-west of the Ranger-camp in the Way of Kings.\n\nRodlam asked you to venture within Haudh Eldacar and defeat the Angmarim within.
Talk to Rodlam in the Way of Kings
Rodlam is at the Ranger-camp in the Way of Kings.\n\nRodlam will want to know that you defeated many Angmarim in Haudh Eldacar.
